"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The UN human rights office condemns an incident as terrible and showing how Palestinians are treated badly in the West Bank.\",            \"english_title\": \"UN Condemns Incident\",            \"translated_version\": \"La oficina de derechos humanos de la ONU dice que un incidente es muy malo y muestra que los palestinos son tratados mal en Cisjordania.\",            \"translated_title\": \"ONU Condena Incidente\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A dissident in Tehran says she feels helpless and under a lot of mental stress.\",            \"english_title\": \"Dissident Feels Helpless\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una disidente en Teher\u00e1n dice que se siente sin ayuda y con mucho estr\u00e9s mental.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Disidente Se Siente Sin Ayuda\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Strait of Hormuz waterway is still closed, causing big problems for global energy shipments.\",            \"english_title\": \"Strait of Hormuz Closed\",            \"translated_version\": \"El estrecho de Ormuz sigue cerrado, causando grandes problemas para los env\u00edos de energ\u00eda en el mundo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Estrecho de Ormuz Cerrado\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Iranian authorities allowed human rights activist Narges Mohammadi to get bail because people are worried about her bad health in prison.\",            \"english_title\": \"Activist Gets Bail\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las autoridades iran\u00edes dejaron que la activista de derechos humanos Narges Mohammadi salga bajo fianza porque la gente est\u00e1 preocupada por su mala salud en la c\u00e1rcel.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Activista Sale Bajo Fianza\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Russian leader sees a chance for Ukraine talks, but criticizes the West for supporting President 